  <brief_title>Identification of Neuromas by High Resolution Ultrasound in Patients With Peripheral Nerve Injury and Amputations</brief_title>
  <official_title>Identification of Neuromas by High Resolution Ultrasound in Patients With Peripheral Nerve Injury and Amputations</official_title>
